{"tha-ap361:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap361:0.2":"Saddasannakavagga ","tha-ap361:0.3":"9 Saranagamaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap361:1.1":"“Aruhimha tada navam, ","tha-ap361:1.2":"bhikkhu cajivako caham; ","tha-ap361:1.3":"Navaya bhijjamanaya, ","tha-ap361:1.4":"bhikkhu me saranam ada. ","tha-ap361:2.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap361:2.2":"yanca me saranam ada; ","tha-ap361:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap361:2.4":"saranagamane phalam. ","tha-ap361:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap361:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap361:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap361:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saranagamaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap361:5.1":"Saranagamaniyattherassapadanam navamam. "}